ive and spore-forming.</s><s>Strictly anaerobic heterotrophs.</s><s>The G+C content of the genomic DNA is about 42 mol%.</s><s>The genus is phylogenetically included in cluster XI of the order <em>Clostridiales</em>, most closely related to the genera <em>Caminicella</em> and <em>Alkaliphilus</em>.</s><s>The type species is <em>Geosporobacter subterraneus</em>.</s></p></content></protolog>